The paper deals with word equations, which are a topic in formal language theory (cs.FL). The algorithmic techniques used in the paper involve data structures and algorithms (cs.DS) such as recompression, which is a technique for compressing strings. The paper also involves complexity analysis (cs.LO) and algorithm design (cs.PL). Finally, the paper deals with solving equations, which is a topic in theoretical computer science (cs.SC).
